{"tid":1980720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共：7人派口罩與10警宵夜同被票控證執法公正","createTime":"2020-04-20T09:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T09:21:43.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9136ff1229b7c4e8f37987c1cff4d3f89b808f","tid":1980720,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"10警元朗宵夜事件 各人違限聚令同被票控<br />\n20.04.2020 16:54<br />\n<br />\n10名休班警員昨日清晨在元朗用饍時，其中一人涉嫌用玻璃樽襲擊女同僚被捕，涉事警員已被停職及獲准保釋候查。10名警員亦因違反限聚令將被票控。<br />\n<br />\n當晚凌晨約4時半，10名警員在元朗屏輝徑一間食肆用膳，施襲的40歲警員懷疑因瑣事與女警爭執，用玻璃樽及手襲擊女警後離去，同日下午涉嫌普通襲擊被捕。警方表示非常重視警員操守，絕不容忍及姑息任何警員違法，定必嚴正處理，進行刑事調查及紀律覆檢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282143&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1282143%26csid%3D261_341&d=Sy1M3c%2BVV8kZ1V6TqBoGPo6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=b71265b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1282143&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"68a25f8d580339024e487980fedad3cd31de1243","tid":1980720,"uid":126731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:12:08.000Z","msg":"派口罩本身合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;公証條毛?"},{"pid":"c97680c19b94b3e95738875a3c904cf5878c9142","tid":1980720,"uid":6132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"告自己人-&gt;罰$2000<br />\n告抗爭者-&gt;暴動罰10年<br />\n港共：執法公正"},{"pid":"49921adeb3556b7ce7c13db359f108b6e4b78c8c","tid":1980720,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"知法犯法"},{"pid":"eabb5bc8df2ffa5e40867e1a6f607380d7a93003","tid":1980720,"uid":25794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"又話派口罩唔計?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085cd9afbe48b55ae15f1df0c78744e1c72